data.description: Amazing two home property on 12 acre mix of trees & pasture. Open concept main home with huge rooms & incredible views throughout. Kitchen features stainless suite including 6 burner gas cooktop, double ovens, large island, hanging pot rack, breakfast bar, dual sinks & pantries. Living features floor to ceiling wood-burning stone fireplace & walls of windows for incredible sunrises & sunsets! Huge primary bedroom on main with sitting or office area. Ensuite bath features antique claw foot soaking tub, walk-in shower, dual vanities & walk-in closets. Upstairs bedrooms with built-ins & walk-in closets. Covered porches, patios, fire pit & festive lighting to enjoy entertaining & relaxing in the shade. Barndominium home is income-producing rental but also perfect setup for guest, multi-gen or caretaker. AG Exempt pasture in pipe fencing & a pond. Property has a $4k per month income potential. Up to $25k seller contribution to buy down interest rate of buyer lending! Owner Financing option!
